    <!-- Theme switch -->
    <div class="theme-switch-wrapper">
        <label class="theme-switch" for="theme-switch">
            <input type="checkbox" id="theme-switch" />
            <span class="slider"></span>
        </label>
    </div>

    <div class="about-intro">
        <h1 class="gradient-text">About Me</h1>
        <div class="intro-text">
            <p class="greeting">Hello World! I'm Soha Farhana 👋</p>
            <p class="tagline">Turning Data into Discoveries, Code into Innovation</p>
            <p class="description">A passionate dual-degree pursuer with an innate talent for conquering complex problems through data science and software engineering. Currently juggling between IIT Madras and NIT Andhra Pradesh, and currently a research intern at IIIT Hyderabad. I'm that rare blend of analytical thinking and creative problem-solving. When I'm not training machine learning models or optimizing algorithms, you'll find me participating in hackathons, turning caffeine into code, and occasionally explaining to my friends why Python is actually named after a snake. 🐍✨</p>
            <div class="skills-highlight">
                <p>What excites me:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>🔬 Data Science & Machine Learning</li>
                    <li>💻 Full Stack Development</li>
                    <li>🎯 Problem Solving</li>
                    <li>🚀 Innovation & Technology</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="coding-profiles">
                    <p>Check out my problem-solving skills:</p>
                    <div class="profiles-container">
                        <a href="https://leetcode.com/u/_Soha_Farhana/" target="_blank" class="profile-link leetcode">
                            <img src="Photos/leetcode-logo.png" alt="LeetCode" class="profile-icon">
                            <span>LeetCode Profile</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.hackerrank.com/profile/sohafarhana" target="_blank" class="profile-link hackerrank">
                            <img src="Photos/github-icon.png" alt="HackerRank" class="profile-icon">
                            <span>HackerRank (4⭐ in SQL, Python, Java, C)</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/user/sohafarhana/" target="_blank" class="profile-link gfg">
                            <img src="Photos/gfg.png" alt="GFG" class="profile-icon">
                            <span>GeeksforGeeks Profile</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="leadership">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <div class="leadership-card">
            <div class="leadership-title">Joint Secretary</div>
            <div class="leadership-org">Computer Science and Engineering Association, NIT Andhra Pradesh</div>
            <div class="leadership-duration">October 2023 – June 2025</div>
            <div class="leadership-desc">As Joint Secretary, I played a key role in organizing technical events, fostering collaboration among students, and promoting a culture of innovation and learning within the department.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="certificates">
        <h2>Certificates</h2>
        <div class="certificates-grid">
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/FoundationCertificate.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/Foundation.png" alt="Foundation Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>IIT Madras Foundation Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Awarded for successful completion of the foundational coursework at IIT Madras, building a strong base in core engineering concepts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/Internship_Infosys.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/internship_infosys.png" alt="Infosys Internship Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>Internship at Infosys</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Recognizes my AI internship at Infosys Springboard, where I worked on real-world AI projects and developed practical skills in artificial intelligence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/ISRO.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/ISRO.png" alt="ISRO Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>ISRO Training Program</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Certificate for participating in ISRO's training program, gaining exposure to space technology and satellite systems.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/sql_basic certificate.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/sql-basic.png" alt="SQL Basic Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>SQL Basic Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Demonstrates my understanding of basic SQL concepts and database management skills.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/sql_intermediate certificate.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/sql-intermediate.png" alt="SQL Intermediate Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>SQL Intermediate Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Shows my proficiency in intermediate SQL queries and database operations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/Nestle.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/nestle.png" alt="Nestle Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>Nestle's e-learning program</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Awarded for completing Nestle's e-learning modules, enhancing my knowledge in food technology and safety.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/adapt.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/adapt.png" alt="ADAPT Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>ADAPT - Algorithms & Data Structures Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Recognizes my achievement in mastering algorithms and data structures through the ADAPT program.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/supervisedlearning.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/ml.png" alt="Supervised Learning Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>Supervised Learning Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Certificate for completing coursework in supervised machine learning techniques and applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/IntrotoAI.pdf">
                    <img src="Photos/IntrotoAI.png" alt="Introduction to AI Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>Introduction to Artificial Intelligence</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Awarded for successfully finishing the Introduction to AI course, covering the basics of artificial intelligence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="certificate-card">
                <a href="Photos/User_ExperienceDesign.png">
                    <img src="Photos/User_ExperienceDesign.png" alt="User Experience Design Certificate" class="certificate-img">
                    <p>User Experience Design Certificate</p>
                </a>
                <p class="explanation">Demonstrates my understanding of user experience principles and design thinking.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

